Use case: Youqi Yang (Phd Student of Walter Dempsey and Ashkan Ertefaei)

A record of the exact data transformations to take MARS MRT curated datasets
into a form that is more easily usable for this particular use case can be found
in the master-workflow.R code in the directory
working-with-ema-and-tracked-app-usage. 

This use case required the same participant decision points as in the MARS
primary aim paper. In addition to EMA data, tracked app usage variables
were a particular interest of this use case. EMA data and visit 1 and 4 data
were also made available.